fields.name: Audi A6 Sedan TFSI e
fields.description: Audi is expanding its portfolio of electrified models consistently: Five powerful models with plug-in hybrid drive are making their debut in the second half of 2019 alone. Presales of the A6 55 TFSI e quattro (combined fuel consumption in l/100 km*: 2.1–1.9; combined energy consumption in kWh/100 km*: 17.9–17.4; combined CO2 emissions in g/km*: 47–43 are starting in Germany. With its system output of 270 kW (367 PS), it delivers a confident performance.
